801fb9aa","tid":622773,"uid":78571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"食完南信, 去石室聖心大教堂<br />\n天主教廣州教區其中一間大教堂<br />\n教堂建於1863年，落成於1888年，歷時25年<br />\n<br />\n外面睇, 幾有feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/182616_576dd361cdcb8853519b467ff0315226.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F182616_576dd361cdcb8853519b467ff0315226.JPG&h=8afafbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/182642_320986bfe97be489101ddbf9d467903d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F182642_320986bfe97be489101ddbf9d467903d.JPG&h=03d4517c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n難得唔使俾入場費, 梗係入去望下坐下啦<br />\n原來都幾大, 係出面睇唔出<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/182730_cd7021af56da45de52fb3d3e8f3fe139.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F182730_cd7021af56da45de52fb3d3e8f3fe139.JPG&h=c6a277fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n入面坐滿人, 但個日係無活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔執輸, 我都坐咗陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/182811_13a8021d6c616804db087d999cfe8d68.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F182811_13a8021d6c616804db087d999cfe8d68.JPG&h=bca20678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彩色玻璃<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/182925_45f167a9afb3a25b4ab2942f046e57a2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F182925_45f167a9afb3a25b4ab2942f046e57a2.JPG&h=d16e8090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾靚<br />\n麻煩巴打頭側一側, 請見諒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/183111_ff4ccf9d7b217c5e045b0a5e43284962.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F183111_ff4ccf9d7b217c5e045b0a5e43284962.JPG&h=8ac9c521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/183231_34af58b1fde5e0d2c2860faf8dabcfb6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F183231_34af58b1fde5e0d2c2860faf8dabcfb6.JPG&h=f7d7f4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/183244_bef192c59e89362ba6643f8747da018e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F183244_bef192c59e89362ba6643f8747da018e.JPG&h=18f2bd33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"146a86c519b9e16a1faaa33f66782127d109f031","tid":622773,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"巴打有無主動同啲大陸妹搭嗲"},{"pid":"58cdf1028d11d1437e514629674063bd077ae2c9","tid":622773,"uid":78571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"下一站---中大 (中山大學)<br />\n廣東省最屈機嘅大學<br />\n<br />\n去到竟然摸門釘, 唔撚俾入<br />\n原來新大學政策唔俾外人入去...上年已經實行<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正門唔俾入, 最後用西門成功入到去<br />\n西門會穿過一堆民居<br />\n一路行都無保安阻止<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/185045_6b85109e6cbaa1aaaa17a4550fcdf574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F185045_6b85109e6cbaa1aaaa17a4550fcdf574.jpg&h=cb9f3dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184115_c63c45f4dc1ad4ed71e63f6269803537.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184115_c63c45f4dc1ad4ed71e63f6269803537.JPG&h=e94c9a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184128_ddf1c2a8432e6c07d57ae2cf56860d59.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184128_ddf1c2a8432e6c07d57ae2cf56860d59.JPG&h=f86def8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184154_ee73e02233e3fb2a496ce2e62bcff099.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184154_ee73e02233e3fb2a496ce2e62bcff099.JPG&h=cd458cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n強國D共享單車好撚戇鳩<br />\n香港電話號碼係租唔到, 屌你老母<br />\n如果租到, 係校園踩下單車, 不失為一種樂趣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184211_a7677b7c90108cc97b55dc8b4b5c904c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184211_a7677b7c90108cc97b55dc8b4b5c904c.JPG&h=5c2be206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n大草地, 聽講係畢業典禮影相必爭之地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184644_f18d6d999ec873653aed916d5a45ae2b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184644_f18d6d999ec873653aed916d5a45ae2b.JPG&h=f459ffed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184814_1c52377a5ea4fa53812bb2f64af61aa8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F184814_1c52377a5ea4fa53812bb2f64af61aa8.JPG&h=a8f5478e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n/<br />\n大部分建築都唔高, 砌磚的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/184832_5503b814e5a08f4feebaec8560355b